"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The agency said that the outbreak, with about 246 cases and 80 deaths, does not qualify as a pandemic emergency.\",            \"english_title\": \"Outbreak Not a Pandemic\",            \"translated_version\": \"La agencia dijo que el brote, con unos 246 casos y 80 muertes, no es una emergencia de pandemia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Brote No es Pandemia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine's president stated that the strikes are a justified response to deadly Russian attacks on Ukrainian cities.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine's Response to Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania dijo que los ataques son una respuesta justa a los ataques mortales rusos en ciudades ucranianas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Respuesta de Ucrania a Ataques\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Staff Sgt Mohamed Mahdhee died during a diving search-and-rescue operation, according to the Maldives government.\",            \"english_title\": \"Diver's Tragic Death\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Sargento Mohamed Mahdhee muri\u00f3 durante una operaci\u00f3n de b\u00fasqueda y rescate de buceo, seg\u00fan el gobierno de Maldivas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muerte Tr\u00e1gica de Buzo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Eight people were injured, four seriously, before bystanders chased and stopped the man.\",            \"english_title\": \"Man Stopped After Injuries\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ocho personas resultaron heridas, cuatro de gravedad, antes de que personas lo persiguieran y detuvieran al hombre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombre Detenido Tras Heridas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"No group has claimed responsibility for the attacks that have destroyed Mussa town in Borno state.\",            \"english_title\": \"No Responsibility for Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ning\u00fan grupo ha dicho ser responsable de los ataques que destruyeron el pueblo de Mussa en el estado de Borno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sin Responsables de Ataques\"        }    ]}"